The repository evaluates publicly released transformer models and public
datasets, all loaded from Hugging Face at pinned commits. Model weights and
source-text content are never redistributed by this repository; the persisted
artifacts are statistical summaries derived from frozen activations and from
benchmark scoring (per-token loss values, observer scores, partial
correlations, exclusive-catch counts, summary statistics).

Per-model license attribution and per-dataset license attribution are recorded
in `results/model_revisions.json` and `results/dataset_revisions.json`. Human-
readable summaries are in `MODELS.md` and `DATA.md`.


